Package: sunflower
Type: Package
Title: Classification of Production Errors, Management of Multiple Attempts Responses, and Computation of Formal Similarity Measures
Version: 22-08-24
Author: Gutiérrez-Cordero, I [aut][cre](<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1508-4203>)
Authors@R: person(
               given = "Ismael",
               family = "Gutiérrez-Cordero",
               role = c("aut", "cre"),
